{
  "stem": "16106.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, we became like brothers and sisters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were like an extended, extended family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, should I meet somebody who was in school, we had so much in common.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Remember the-- the teachers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were like brothers and sisters, really.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was very-- a very close relationship.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And our class [INAUDIBLE], our class mother, we would call it, was for Dr.-- Mrs.-- Dr., for Dr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Weinright. ?] We called her Tante [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Push. ?] And she went with us, again, from beginning to end, and so on, on and on and on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The my-- my first teacher was a-- a wonderful teacher.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was in preschool.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Her name was Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Herma-- Fraulein Herma.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Miss Herma.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I remember a very, very-- [BACKROUND NOISE] I remember very well because I was always such a big child.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I was bigger than any other child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when the parents came to pick up their children, they used to compare, yes?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And here I came, that big slob, and says, now which grade are you?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, I'm in the four class.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is pre-school.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used to stare at me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Fraulein Herma used to come running. 'Yes, she is in pre-school, but she's still young.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Still young.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [LAUGHS] the next time somebody asked me, which grade are you, my little-- my child?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I am in pre-school, but I am young!",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And that sort of caused a lot of amusement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know when I said it, it was-- it was funny.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the teacher said it, was accepted very easily.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] So I was still young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would like to stay that way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We studied?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Languages.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Quite a few.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had, first of all, German as, as a, as a language.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
